вҹҰ Test that helper functions are now allowed вҹ§

вҹҰ Utility function used by multiple functions вҹ§
О»is_positive(x:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=x>0

О»main()вҶ’рқ•Ҡ=process_a(50)++" and "++process_b(-5)

О»process_a(x:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ•Ҡ match is_positive(x){
  trueвҶ’"positive"|
  falseвҶ’"negative"
}

О»process_b(y:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ•Ҡ match is_positive(y){
  trueвҶ’"yes"|
  falseвҶ’"no"
}
